    <abstract id="aspace_f3bfa84fd08ffc2c101a8361f84a964f" label="Abstract">The Allegheny County Bureau of Air Pollution Control Records contains materials related to smoke control and air pollution. It includes minutes of the County Smoke Control Advisory Committee; annual reports and ordinances for Pittsburgh and Allegheny County; research, studies and informational reports from Pittsburgh Bureau of Smoke Prevention, County Bureau of Air Pollution Control, the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency, and other organizations on pollution concerns.</abstract>
